cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the problem of detecting fake news on Twitter, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves social media analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The use of datasets and feature analysis suggests the involvement of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
